## Derived files (Pearl ISC applies)

Pearl `zk-pow` STARK-circuit chips + AIRs, ported to Plonky3:

  * `src/composite_full_air.rs`          — Port of `Pearl zk-pow pearl_air.rs`
  * `src/composite_trace.rs`             — Port of `Pearl zk-pow pearl_trace.rs`
  * `src/composite_preprocess.rs`        — Port of `Pearl zk-pow pearl_preprocess.rs`
  * `src/chips/range_table.rs`           — Port of `Pearl zk-pow chip/range_table.rs`
  * `src/chips/stark_row.rs`             — Port of `Pearl zk-pow chip/monotonic_increment.rs`
  * `src/chips/control.rs`               — Port of `Pearl zk-pow chip/control_and_matid_packed.rs`
  * `src/chips/i8u8.rs`                  — Port of `Pearl zk-pow chip/i8u8.rs`
  * `src/chips/input.rs`                 — Port of `Pearl zk-pow chip/input/constraints.rs`
  * `src/chips/blake3/mod.rs`            — Port of `Pearl zk-pow chip/blake3/`
  * `src/chips/blake3/layout.rs`         — Port of `Pearl zk-pow chip/blake3/blake3_layout.rs`
  * `src/chips/blake3/logic.rs`          — Port of `Pearl zk-pow chip/blake3/logic.rs`
  * `src/chips/blake3/compress.rs`       — Port of `Pearl zk-pow chip/blake3/blake3_compress.rs`
  * `src/chips/blake3/round_ops.rs`      — Port of `Pearl zk-pow chip/blake3/blake3_air.rs` (constraint primitives)
  * `src/chips/blake3/round_air.rs`      — Port of `Pearl zk-pow chip/blake3/blake3_air.rs` (round AIR composition)
  * `src/chips/blake3/chip.rs`           — Port of `Pearl zk-pow chip/blake3/blake3_air.rs` (top-level chip)
  * `src/chips/jackpot/mod.rs`           — Port of `Pearl zk-pow chip/jackpot/`
  * `src/chips/jackpot/chip.rs`          — Port of `Pearl zk-pow chip/jackpot/jackpot_air.rs`
  * `src/chips/jackpot/compute.rs`       — Port of `Pearl zk-pow chip/jackpot/` arithmetic
  * `src/chips/matmul/mod.rs`            — Port of `Pearl zk-pow chip/matmul/`
  * `src/chips/matmul/chip.rs`           — Port of `Pearl zk-pow chip/matmul/`
  * `src/chips/matmul/compute.rs`        — Port of `Pearl zk-pow chip/matmul/` arithmetic

